document_data.name: Setana
document_data.Activities: Around [[1370 DR]], Setana worked as a barmaid for [[Gallowshawk]], earning some notoriety for the inn. Secretly, she was also a [[Harper]] agent. She was bound to a golden hair comb. A very frequent guest was the unusual [[mind flayer]] [[Sangalor]].
document_data.History: In life, Setana was very devoted to her mistress, who gave her the comb. When Setana died at sea, she had with her the comb, which was later recovered by an [[aquatic elf]], who traded it to the captain of the ill-fated ship on which Gallowshawk had worked. The comb was the only piece that he had not sold over the years.
